rComments: Quite Easily the best prof i had this semester, would take her class again. Gives good feedback and makes class interesting and fun. Would take her again

You will learn more in one semester than you ever thought possible.  A renowned academic with a passion for research and writing, as well as a superb lecturer.  She offers very helpful feedback and is genuinely invested in student success.

Lori G. Beaman is the best professor ever.  She is passionate about her work and keeps all students enaged in higher learning.  She demands a lot from her students, especially in terms of reading, but it is all for the better.  You will learn a true sense of excellence from this amazing professor.
